      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Oliver Brausch</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:167px;\"><a href=\"http://radaris.de/p/Oliver/Brausch/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/9/90/OliverBrausch.jpg\" width=\"165\" height=\"236\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:OliverBrausch.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Oliver Brausch <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Oliver Brausch</b>,<br />\na German physicist, computer scientist, and IT-architect. He holds a Ph.D. in physics from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Bayreuth\">University of Bayreuth</a> on the topic of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rayleigh%E2%80%93B%C3%A9nard_convection\">Rayleigh–Bénard convection</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> . As avocational computer chess programmer, Oliver is author of <a href=\"/OliThink\" title=\"OliThink\">OliThink</a>, an <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> with <a href=\"/C\" title=\"C\">C</a> and <a href=\"/Java\" title=\"Java\">Java</a> versions available <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> , whose <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">evaluation</a> consists almost of <a href=\"/Material\" title=\"Material\">material balance</a> and <a href=\"/Mobility\" title=\"Mobility\">mobility</a>. \nOliver's stance to mobility was likely due to his background in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Statistical_physics\">statistical physics</a> concerning <a href=\"/Papa#Entropy\" title=\"Papa\">entropy</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2007_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2007 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Oliver_Brausch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Brausch</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i>Rayleigh-Bénard Konvektion in verschiedenen isotropen und anisotropen Systemen</i>. Ph.D. thesis, Institute of Physics, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Bayreuth\">University of Bayreuth</a>, advisor <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.pesch.physik.uni-bayreuth.de/de/index.html\">Werner Pesch</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.scholarpedia.org/article/User:A._V._Getling\">A. V. Getling</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Brausch</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>Cellular flow patterns and their evolutionary scenarios in three-dimensional Rayleigh–Bénard convection</i>. DOI: 10.1103/PhysRevE.67.046313, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://brausch.org/home/PRE_046313_v67_2003.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=-sRK_ysAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Karen E. Daniels</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Brausch</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.pesch.physik.uni-bayreuth.de/de/index.html\">Werner Pesch</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eberhard_Bodenschatz\">Eberhard Bodenschatz</a> (<b>2007</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://arxiv.org/abs/nlin/0702006v1\">Competition and bistability of ordered undulations and undulation chaos in inclined layer convection</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://arxiv.org/PS_cache/nlin/pdf/0702/0702006v1.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Oliver_Brausch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2007_...\">2007 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Oliver_Brausch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2007 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=166649&amp;t=18750\">Re: Question about SEE (Static exchange evaluation)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Brausch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 18, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/X-ray_Attacks_(Bitboards)\" title=\"X-ray Attacks (Bitboards)\">X-ray Attacks</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=18854\">Problem with Transposition Table and Repitition-Draw</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Brausch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 11, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a>, <a href=\"/Repetitions\" title=\"Repetitions\">Repetitions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=19273\">The limits of \"Just-mobility-evaluation\"</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Brausch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 29, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=30793\">OliThink GUI in Java... Complete source posted</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Brausch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 25, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a>, <a href=\"/Java\" title=\"Java\">Java</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Oliver_Brausch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=31494\">The problem with LMR in suprtactical positions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Brausch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 05, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=31505\">Problem with exploding tree because of extensions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Brausch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 05, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Search_Explosion\" title=\"Search Explosion\">Search Explosion</a>, <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=42664\">OliThink 5.3.1 released (Win, Mac, Linux and Java)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Brausch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 28, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=42714\">OliThink 5.3.2 released (Source, Windows, Mac and Linux)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Brausch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 02, 2012</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Oliver_Brausch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=74203\">OliThink 5.4.0 has been published with an big leap in strength for only 3 lines of code</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Brausch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 16, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/OliThink\" title=\"OliThink\">OliThink</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=74256\">Java vs C. It's not like one would think</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Brausch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 22, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Java\" title=\"Java\">Java</a>, <a href=\"/C\" title=\"C\">C</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=74498\">Null move pruning = lottery?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Brausch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 18, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=74503\">Looking for automatic Engine Testing Software</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Brausch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 19, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Engine_Testing\" title=\"Engine Testing\">Engine Testing</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=74821\">An undetected bug for 10 years</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Brausch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 18, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Diagonals#TwoSquares\" title=\"Diagonals\">Two Squares on a Diagonal</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=75040\">Is cloning a hobby?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Brausch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 07, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75060\">Official Release of OliThink 5.7.5 including a Java-GUI</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Brausch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 09, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=75308\">Performance loss when removing unused function</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Brausch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 05, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=75525\">Different performance of equal executables</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Brausch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 24, 2020</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Oliver_Brausch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://brausch.org/home/\">Oliver Brausch Homepage</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://radaris.de/p/Oliver/Brausch/\">Radaris: Oliver Brausch</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Oliver_Brausch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://radaris.de/p/Oliver/Brausch/\">Radaris: Oliver Brausch</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Oliver Brausch</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i>Rayleigh-Bénard Konvektion in verschiedenen isotropen und anisotropen Systemen</i>. Ph.D. thesis, Institute of Physics, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Bayreuth\">University of Bayreuth</a>, advisor <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.pesch.physik.uni-bayreuth.de/de/index.html\">Werner Pesch</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://brausch.org/home/chess/index.html\">Oliver Brausch Homepage | Chess Downloads</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.fakultaet1.uni-bayreuth.de/de/research/01_dissertationen_und_habilitationen/\">Dissertationen und Habilitationen | Fakultät für Mathematik, Physik, Informatik | Universität Bayreuth</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://brausch.org/home/\">Oliver Brausch Homepage</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rayleigh%E2%80%93B%C3%A9nard_convection\">Rayleigh–Bénard convection from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 2026030